{"tid":1649933,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔再推所有蛋糕post","createTime":"2019-10-12T19:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T19:06:34.000Z","uid":40551,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"99ee44b89525671d00e53450b2f35fa51f7da1b8","tid":1649933,"uid":40551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:02:30.000Z","msg":"DNLM班人喺靈堂隔離切蛋係痴線 係唔啱timing 係過份 係戇鳩<br />\n但果班人唔識做人 點解我地要學佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地之前成日俾外媒讚學習能力高，但唔係呢方面嘅學習能力喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要記得獨立思考我地嘅言行 我地嘅方向啊！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n唔係齋講架！<br />\n<br />\n不割𥱊 不篤灰 不分化<br />\n唔係齋講架！<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個運動 呢個革命 因為一個蛋糕而失敗...我地點樣笑陳同佳，以後對家都係咁樣笑返我地...<br />\n<br />\n希望聽朝起身 熱門同時事台 全部都係行動post，而唔再係點樣聲討班戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbabc77a9f3653252d9f555c2d947cf7c89a4f3","tid":1649933,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:03:00.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d5a01c749a03a6df97e5a8e2d9b6ba95cdcdd02b","tid":1649933,"uid":135349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GA9PvQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GA9PvQ.jpg&h=7cfaa9cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a178c634cf25c9b052516494ecf135fff576f3dd","tid":1649933,"uid":40551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:04:36.000Z","msg":"聽日！18區開花啦喂！"},{"pid":"516b9f84af815b3c97175908c1454a1278b66bc9","tid":1649933,"uid":318505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mKze0C4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm